Reference

All functions

ChickWeight

Weight versus age of chicks on different diets

astatur.all.used.packages

List of all R-packages that are used in the book.

condisc()

Measurement model validity

deaths

Number of deaths in Norway by age in single-year bins.

depression

Data from a web-based intervention study for depression.

depression.wide

Data from a web-based intervention study for depression converted into wide-format from the dataset depression.

diet

Contains information on persons undergoing one of three different kinds of diets. https://www.sheffield.ac.uk/polopoly_fs/1.536445!/file/MASH_ANOVA_in_R.pdf

epi.bfi

13 personality scales from the Eysenck Personality Inventory and Big 5 inventory

flats

Prices of apartments in 2013, Trondheim, Norway.

msq

75 mood items from the Motivational State Questionnaire for 3896 participants

newStudents

Number of new students in Norway by year, age and gender

olympic

Basic bio data on athletes and medal results from Summer Games in Rio 2016.

present

Price of birthday presents.

regression.diagnostics()

Regression diagnostics.

relicoef()

Raykov's factor reliability coefficient

stroop

Single-trial responses from a Stroop task (85 subjs).

studentHeights

Body-height in cm collected from a statistics course at a Norwegian university across three years.

theme_astatur()

Theme used for "Applied Statistics using R".

theme_spss()

Theme that looks a bit like SPSS.

titanic

Titanic Passenger Survival Data Set. This dataset has been re-packaged for convenience from https://github.com/paulhendricks/titanic

values

The data was obtained from a survey of 1004 Norwegian individuals. In this survey, the respondents were asked to indicate (on an ordinal scale from 1 = not at all important, to 5 = very important) how important each of five personal values was as a guiding principle in their lives.

vimp()

Predictor relative importance

workout

Data from a survey in a fitness center in Trondheim.

workout2

Data from a survey in a fitness center in Trondheim. Questions were of the form "How important is it to workout ..."

workout3

Data from 6 Questions from a survey in a fitness center in Trondheim (2014). Questions were of the form "I am training ..."
